---
title: Sizzling Steak Taco Bar Elevated Dinners, Impressively Easy
description: Prep, sizzle, zap, serve: Four easy steps to our fastest, freshest weeknight meal yet. Thanks to a few clever time-savers from our chefs, you and yours will be bellying up to your own steak taco bar in just 15 minutes! Quick-sear sliced steak with pepper, onion, and spices; then squeeze on the lime juice, set out the fixins—warm tortillas, pico de gallo, guacamole, cheese, and red pepper crema—and everyone can build their own fresh, flavorful dinner in a flash!
